# ANTI-CHEAT — WHAT WORKS AND WHAT DOESN'T

# EAC (Easy Anti-Cheat) and BattlEye — both have native linux/proton
# support since 2021. game developers OPT IN per-title. so "EAC is
# linux-compatible" doesn't mean every EAC game works on linux —
# only the ones whose developer enabled the linux build.
#
# WHAT WORKS:
#   - Apex Legends (until 2024; reverted, then back; check current)
#   - Apex spinoffs, Hunt: Showdown, Dead by Daylight, Elden Ring
#     (under proton), Squad, Dying Light 2, many others
