# the canonical lookup is PROTONDB.COM. paste a game name, see
# community reports + medal rating + workarounds.


# PROTONDB — THE COMMUNITY DATABASE

# before assuming a game works (or doesn't), check protondb.com.
# every popular game has community reports:
#
#   Platinum — works perfectly, no tweaks
#   Gold     — works perfectly after minor tweaks
#   Silver   — works with minor issues
#   Bronze   — runs but with significant issues
#   Borked   — does not run / unplayable
#
# the reports often include exact Proton version + launch options that
# work. read 2-3 recent reports for any game you're unsure about.


# BAZZITE — FEDORA-BASED IMMUTABLE GAMING OS

# bazzite is uBlue's gaming-focused atomic fedora derivative (built
# on silverblue/kinoite). preconfigured with:
#   - steam + proton + gamescope + mangohud + lutris + heroic
#   - nvidia or AMD drivers prebaked
#   - controllers configured
#   - HDR + VRR support out of the box
